author: Reuters Editorial
title: Number of infected crew on U.S. aircraft carrier rises to 155: Navy
description: The number of crew on the USS Theodore Roosevelt aircraft carrier who have tested positive for the coronavirus has risen 13% in the past 24 hours to 155, the Navy said on Saturday, in the wake of the firing of the carrier's captain.
content:
